metadata.name: #1 Rabbit
metadata.description: For pinkmons, perseverance appears as an ox, sharpness appears in the appearance of a bird, peace appears as a pig, confidence appears as a cat, wisdom appears as a monkey, caution appears as a rabbit, loyalty appears as a dog, brave appears as a leopard. Some pinkmons have more than two positive personalities at the same time, and their appearance will be like a mixture of many animals.
